TurboMind AI Splash Screen
==========================

This file should be replaced with an actual splash.png file.

Requirements:
- Size: 1024x1024 pixels
- Format: PNG
- Should display app name and loading indicator
- Name: splash.png

To add your splash screen:
1. Create splash.png (1024x1024)
2. Replace this file with your splash.png
3. Update buildozer.spec: presplash.filename = assets/splash.png

For now, this is a placeholder.
